data.description: Eclectic Cape Cod on 3+ acres in Granville Schools. Built in 1912 and  artistically updated. The main home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, gourmet kitchen with SS appliances and granite counters. In the basement you'll find the perfect spot for a 2nd den or cozy TV space. Brand new whole house water filtration system including a reverse osmosis system for drinking. Do you like long hot showers? This home as an instant hot water heater! New metal roof to boot! The Barn has been transformed into the ultimate entertainment space with water and sewer rough-ins. Beautiful glass industrial garage door opens up to view the back acreage. The 2nd floor of the barn is ready to be customized!. See A2A for more!
